g.text: Inheritance tree of super classes starting from package

a.title: ― DataSet: Organized collection of data based on keys.
a.xlink:title: ― DataSet: Organized collection of data based on keys.

a.title: ― DataStructure: Data organization based on reusable data structure components.
a.xlink:title: ― DataStructure: Data organization based on reusable data structure components.

a.title: ― Datum: Correspondence of a data instance to the concept it represents.
a.xlink:title: ― Datum: Correspondence of a data instance to the concept it represents.

a.title: ― InstanceValue: Single data instance corresponding to a concept (with a notion of equality defined) being observed, captured, or derived.
a.xlink:title: ― InstanceValue: Single data instance corresponding to a concept (with a notion of equality defined) being observed, captured, or derived.

a.title: ― DimensionalDataSet: Organized collection of multidimensional data. It is structured by a dimensional data structure.
a.xlink:title: ― DimensionalDataSet: Organized collection of multidimensional data. It is structured by a dimensional data structure.

a.title: ― RevisableDatum: A datum that can be qualified by a revision.
a.xlink:title: ― RevisableDatum: A datum that can be qualified by a revision.

a.title: ― DimensionalKeyMember: Single data instance that is part of a dimensional key.
a.xlink:title: ― DimensionalKeyMember: Single data instance that is part of a dimensional key.

a.title: ― KeyValueDataStore: Organized collection of key-value data. It is structured by a key value structure.
a.xlink:title: ― KeyValueDataStore: Organized collection of key-value data. It is structured by a key value structure.

a.title: ― ContextualComponent: Encapsulates contextual information of the key-value datastore to provide a scope to the instance key. The instance key is unique within the scope.
a.xlink:title: ― ContextualComponent: Encapsulates contextual information of the key-value datastore to provide a scope to the instance key. The instance key is unique within the scope.

a.title: ― SyntheticIdComponent: Persistent and unique identifier (PIDs) to provide standarized, long-lasting identification.
a.xlink:title: ― SyntheticIdComponent: Persistent and unique identifier (PIDs) to provide standarized, long-lasting identification.

a.title: ― InstanceKey: Single-valued key representation produced from the merge of the representations of all key members and a descriptor.
a.xlink:title: ― InstanceKey: Single-valued key representation produced from the merge of the representations of all key members and a descriptor.

a.title: ― MainKeyMember: Identifies the unit of interest, either a statistical unit or a population, via identifier or dimension components, respectively, plus an optional contextual component. If neither identifier nor dimension components are present, then a synthetic id component is used.
a.xlink:title: ― MainKeyMember: Identifies the unit of interest, either a statistical unit or a population, via identifier or dimension components, respectively, plus an optional contextual component. If neither identifier nor dimension components are present, then a synthetic id component is used.

a.title: ― LongDataSet: Organized collection of long data. It is structured by a long data structure.
a.xlink:title: ― LongDataSet: Organized collection of long data. It is structured by a long data structure.

a.title: ― Descriptor: Use of a code for variable identification in the context of a data structure and a variable descriptor component.
a.xlink:title: ― Descriptor: Use of a code for variable identification in the context of a data structure and a variable descriptor component.

a.title: ― LongMainKeyMember: Single data instance that is part of a long key.
a.xlink:title: ― LongMainKeyMember: Single data instance that is part of a long key.

a.title: ― ReferenceValue: Recorded value in a variable value component. Value referenced by a descriptor.
a.xlink:title: ― ReferenceValue: Recorded value in a variable value component. Value referenced by a descriptor.

a.title: ― WideDataSet: Organized collection of wide data. It is structured by a wide data structure.
a.xlink:title: ― WideDataSet: Organized collection of wide data. It is structured by a wide data structure.

a.title: ― WideKeyMember: Single data instance that is part of a wide key.
a.xlink:title: ― WideKeyMember: Single data instance that is part of a wide key.

a.title: ― DataStructureComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure.
a.xlink:title: ― DataStructureComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure.

a.title: ― AttributeComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure to qualify observations or provide other types of supplementary information.
a.xlink:title: ― AttributeComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure to qualify observations or provide other types of supplementary information.

a.title: ― DimensionComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a dimensional data structure to identify the universes associated with data points. The variable acts as a field in the compound identifier (the key structure) to disambiguate the cells in the multi-dimensional "cube".
a.xlink:title: ― DimensionComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a dimensional data structure to identify the universes associated with data points. The variable acts as a field in the compound identifier (the key structure) to disambiguate the cells in the multi-dimensional "cube".

a.title: ― IdentifierComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a long or wide data structure to identify the units associated to data points, and in dimensional and key value data structures to provide identifying fields for the instance values.
a.xlink:title: ― IdentifierComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a long or wide data structure to identify the units associated to data points, and in dimensional and key value data structures to provide identifying fields for the instance values.

a.title: ― MeasureComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure to hold the observed/derived values.
a.xlink:title: ― MeasureComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure to hold the observed/derived values.

a.title: ― VariableDescriptorComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure to provide codes for variable identification.
a.xlink:title: ― VariableDescriptorComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure to provide codes for variable identification.

a.title: ― VariableValueComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure to record values of multiple variables.
a.xlink:title: ― VariableValueComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a data structure to record values of multiple variables.

a.title: ― KeyMember: Single data instance that is part of a key.
a.xlink:title: ― KeyMember: Single data instance that is part of a key.
